title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-04-2014 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-04-2014 TUES....PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program



    The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



     
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 2/4/14Tuesday, February 04, 2014


Glenn kicks off the show with a long discussion with Texas Senator Ted Cruz,
   to discuss the many ways the state of Texas is suing the Obama Administration
     to stop the encroaching of states rights.

  Also, the heartwarming story of a kid and his mother's life and death
            challenges thanks to Obamacare.

  Plus, Texas Attorney General Gregg Abbot joins the program
        to discuss the many fights Texas is waging against Obama in court.
